---
<section id="clientes" class="relative py-28 lg:py-40 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-surface via-brand/[0.02] to-surface dark:from-surface-dark dark:via-brand/[0.03] dark:to-surface-dark" />
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black tracking-tighter text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
        Lo que dicen <span class="text-brand">nuestros clientes</span>
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-20 lg:mb-24">
      <div class="p-1.5 rounded-[2rem] bg-border dark:bg-border-dark">
        <div class="rounded-[calc(2rem-0.375rem)] p-8 bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-1 text-brand">
            {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" /></svg>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-muted-dark leading-relaxed">"Siempre me entregan a tiempo y la arena azul es de la mejor calidad. Los recomiendo para cualquier obra."</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <img src="/images/testimonial-1.jpg" alt="Carlos M." class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" />
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark text-sm">Carlos M.</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Contratista, Santo Domingo</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-1.5 rounded-[2rem] bg-border dark:bg-border-dark">
        <div class="rounded-[calc(2rem-0.375rem)] p-8 bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-1 text-brand">
            {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" /></svg>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-muted-dark leading-relaxed">"El itabo que compré para mi proyecto fue excelente. El camión de 20mt me rindió perfecto para los cimientos."</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <img src="/images/testimonial-2.jpg" alt="Roberto P." class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" />
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark text-sm">Roberto P.</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Ingeniero civil, San Cristóbal</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-1.5 rounded-[2rem] bg-border dark:bg-border-dark">
        <div class="rounded-[calc(2rem-0.375rem)] p-8 bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark space-y-4">
          <div class="flex gap-1 text-brand">
            {[1,2,3,4,5].map(() => (
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z" /></svg>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted dark:text-muted-dark leading-relaxed">"Grava de primera y el servicio de entrega es puntual. Llevo 3 años trabajando con ellos."</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <img src="/images/testimonial-3.jpg" alt="Miguel A." class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover" />
            <div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-ink dark:text-ink-dark text-sm">Miguel A.</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">Maestro constructor, Baní</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-10">
        Clientes que <span class="text-brand">confían</span> en nosotros
      </h3>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center font-black text-brand text-sm">C</div>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold">ConstruRoca</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center font-black text-brand text-sm">H</div>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold">Hormigones del Sur</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center font-black text-brand text-sm">PV</div>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold">Pavimentos Viales</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-muted dark:text-muted-dark">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center font-black text-brand text-sm">E</div>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold">Edifica RD</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
